flowchart TD
    Start([User Request]) --> Parse[Parse Request]

    Parse --> Hooks{Pre-Request Hooks}
    Hooks -->|Allow| Build[Build Discovery]
    Hooks -->|Deny| Reject([Reject Request])

    Build --> Model[LLM Model]
    Model --> Tools{Select Tools}

    Tools -->|Tool Call| Sandbox[Execute in Sandbox]
    Sandbox -->|Result| HooksPT{Post-Tool Hooks}
    HooksPT -->|Continue| Model

    Tools -->|Final Response| Compact[Compaction Check]
    Compact -->|Compact if needed| Memory[Update Memory]
    Memory --> Session[Update Session]
    Session --> UI[Render UI]
    UI --> End([Response to User])

    style Reject fill:#ff6b6b
    style Sandbox fill:#4ecdc4